<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٩٠٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6700">أَبُو الْوَلِيدِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1114">جَبَلَةَ بْنِ سُحَيْمٍ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنَ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> يَقُولُ: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«الشَّهْرُ هَكَذَا وَهَكَذَا وَخَنَسَ الْإِبْهَامَ فِي الثَّالِثَةِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>